Annie: This is a lot. We'd better read it carefully to make sure it's all in line with what we've been taught.

::fba3_checklist_display [display=target:psych_sba_sidebar4auto label="View Fidelity Checklist"]

Lin: And here's a fidelity checklist we can give to Annie's roommate. It covers the bedtime routine steps.

JJ: I added some items about how to respond to escape behaviors, too. [face=explaining]

